1.	Lighting
  https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/class/Lighting
  
  ※참고 : https://devforum.roblox.com/t/how-to-get-professional-lighting-for-beginners/625593
  
  Lighting  - Technology   => ShadowMap 설정을 해야 효과적



GetSunDirection() => 태양 방향 변경
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/function/Lighting/GetSunDirection

Ambient => 조명 색상 변경
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/Ambient

Brightness => 조명 농도 변경
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/Brightness

ClockTime => 조명 애니메이션 (낮 <-> 밤)
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/ClockTime

FogColor => 안개 색상 변경
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/FogColor

FogStart & FogEnd => 안개 범위 (FogStart : 15, FogEnd : 50 테스트)
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/FogStart
https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/api-reference/property/Lighting/FogEnd




